Interface Provider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FacebookProvider, GoogleProvider

    public interface Provider
extends Resource
    A provider resource holds specific information needed to work with Provider-based Directories (e.g, Google and Facebook).
